" Window movement
map <C-j> <C-w>j<CR>
map <C-k> <C-w>k<CR>
map <C-h> <C-w>h<CR>
map <C-l> <C-w>l<CR>

" Comments
vmap gc :xccmd commentAndUncommentCurrentLines<CR>
nmap gc :xccmd commentAndUncommentCurrentLines<CR>

" Testing
nmap <SPACE>a :xccmd testActiveRunContext<CR>

" Directions work the way I like
nmap j gj
nmap k gk
vmap j gj
vmap k gk

" Create a new file
nmap <SPACE>f :xccmd newDocument<CR>

" Run the project
nmap <SPACE>r :run<CR>

" When jumping, go to the first non whitespace character
set startofline
